             </span>
            </a>
           </h2>
          </header>
          <div class="node__content clearfix">
           <div class="clearfix text-formatted field field--name-body field--type-text-with-summary field--label-hidden field__item">
            <h2>
             <strong>
              In the Crosshairs: When You’re the Target of Nation-State Cyberattacks
             </strong>
            </h2>
            <div class="gt-header-right">
             <p>
              <strong>
               Georgia Tech Research Institute Conference Center
              </strong>
              <br/>
              250 14th Street, NW, Atlanta, GA 30318-9108
             </p>
            </div>
            <p>
             <strong>
              October 4, 2018
              <br/>
              8:30 a.m. — 5:00 p.m.
             </strong>
            </p>
           </div>
          </div>
         </article>
        </div>
       </div>
      </div>
      <nav aria-labelledby="block-menu2018forumsubmenu-menu" class="block block-menu navigation menu--menu-2018-forum-submenu" id="block-menu2018forumsubmenu" role="navigation">
